OL,4,Cblack hole, warns leading think tank
OL,6,FThe National Institute for Economic
OL,7,Fand Social Research (NIESR) has called
OL,8,Fit.
OL,10,FIn its view, tax rises this autumn are
OL,11,Fnot just likely, they're inevitable.
OL,12,FAnd more than that, it believes the
OL,13,Fgovernment will have to break a
OL,14,Fcentral promise it made to voters at
OL,15,Fthe last election.
