OL,6,FBack in March, the government's
OL,7,Fofficial forecaster ` the Office for
OL,8,FBudget Responsibility ` thought the
OL,9,Fchancellor would just hit that target,
OL,10,Fwith #9.9 billion of headroom to
OL,11,Fspare, a very small margin.
OL,13,FNIESR now thinks Rachel Reeves will
OL,14,Fmiss it by #41.2 billion.
OL,16,FThat's not just a miss - it's a very
OL,17,Fbig hole.
