OL,3,CReeves must raise taxes to cover #41bn
OL,4,Cblack hole, warns leading think tank
OL,6,F"All forecasts are wrong, we know
OL,7,Fthat," said Stephen Millard, NIESR's
OL,8,FDeputy Director for
OL,9,FMacroeconomics."But I'm fairly
OL,10,Fconvinced that there's a sizeable gap
OL,11,Fthe chancellor will need to fill. It
OL,12,Fmight not be #50 billion - it could be
OL,13,F#40 billion."
OL,15,FLabour's 2024 manifesto promised no
OL,16,Ftax rises for "working people" and no
OL,17,Fincreases to National Insurance, or
OL,18,Fthe basic, higher or additional rates
OL,19,Fof income tax or VAT.
