OL,4,Cblack hole, warns leading think tank
OL,6,FNIESR believes that pledge is no
OL,7,Flonger sustainable.
OL,9,FMillard says the Chancellor now faces
OL,10,Fan "impossible trilemma": rewrite the
OL,11,Fborrowing rules; cut public spending;
OL,12,For raise taxes.
OL,14,FIn his view, investors already see the
OL,15,FUK as a riskier bet and charge higher
OL,16,Frates of interest than before, and
OL,17,Fdepartmental budgets have only just
OL,18,Fbeen set, making tax rises the only
OL,19,Frealistic option left.
