OL,4,Cblack hole, warns leading think tank
OL,6,FNIESR recommends that the government
OL,7,Frepair the public finances with "a
OL,8,Fmoderate but sustained increase in
OL,9,Ftaxes".
OL,11,FIt estimates the chancellor could
OL,12,Fraise #8 billion a year by freezing
OL,13,Fthe thresholds of income tax and
OL,14,Fnational insurance beyond April 2028.
OL,16,FNIESR points out that raising #50
OL,17,Fbillion a year would require a 5
OL,18,Fpercentage point increase in both the
OL,19,Fbasic and higher rates of income tax,
OL,20,Falthough this is not something it
OL,21,Frecommends.
