OL,6,FIn a statement, the Treasury said:
OL,7,F"The OBR (Office for Budget
OL,8,FResponsibility) will publish an
OL,9,Fupdated medium-term forecast alongside
OL,10,Fthe Autumn Budget ` we will not
OL,11,Fspeculate on their forecast."
OL,13,F"As set out in the Plan for Change,
OL,14,Fthe best way to strengthen public
OL,15,Ffinances is by growing the economy `
OL,16,Fwhich is our focus. Thanks to our
OL,17,Fplanning reforms, the OBR has said
OL,18,Fthat the economy is expected to grow
OL,19,Fby the end of the decade."
